Description: SphinxFolders
        =============
        
        Sphinx directive to list the content of a folder
        
        Sample usage::
        
        
            .. folder:: _static/demo_folder
                :class: folder
                :desc_ext: .desc
                :glob: *.pdf
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
